{"type":"text","timestamp":1781418053185,"sessionID":"ses_13b36ae6fffeLx31BHseD4QV23","part":{"id":"prt_ec4ca4bfa001VBpjFm4IuwLHYc","messageID":"msg_ec4ca1bee001RYjiABcTZshRlJ","sessionID":"ses_13b36ae6fffeLx31BHseD4QV23","type":"text","text":"The skill contract confirms this must follow the deep-research loop state model: read state first, write iteration markdown plus JSONL deltas, check convergence each iteration, then synthesize. I’ll inspect only the requested lineage directory state before writing.","time":{"start":1781418052602,"end":1781418053184},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_08ad496061672d25016a2e484492508191845cc923d137e27e","phase":"commentary"}}}}
